comments: Mills (BKN) briefly engages with Adebayo (MIA) in the post but the marginal contact does not affect his FOM.
Sharpe (BKN) puts an arm around Adebayo (MIA) during the rebound but releases and the contact does not affect his ability to get to the rebound.
Lowry (MIA) places both hands on Thomas (BKN) during the drive to the basket and the contact affects his SQBR.
Edwards (BKN) briefly engages with Butler (MIA) but disengages and the contact does not affect his FOM.
Adebayo (MIA) firms up in a screening position in Edwards' (BKN) path and does not deliver contact.
Irving (BKN) swipes down and avoids making contact with Lowry's (MIA) arm during his jump shot attempt.
Adebayo (MIA) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Edwards (BKN) and does not deliver contact.  Edwards loses his balance on his own as he goes around the screen.
Mills (BKN) makes contact to Adebayo's (MIA) arm that prevents him from controlling the pass.
Edwards (BKN) loses his balance upon gathering the loose ball and any contact with Adebayo (MIA) is incidental.
Tucker (MIA) legally contests Irving's (BKN) jump shot attempt.  Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Thomas (BKN) has a marginal hand placed on Butler's (MIA) back but the contact does not impede him as he elevates for the pass.
Thomas (BKN) places his off-arm against Lowry (MIA) and the contact is marginal as he releases.
Adebayo (MIA) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Edwards (BKN) and does not deliver contact.
Sharpe (BKN) jumps vertically and maintains a legal vertical position contesting the play at the basket by Butler (MIA).
As Irving (BKN) moves towards Tucker (MIA), Tucker steps into his path and initiates foot to foot contact that affects Irving's SQBR.
Edwards (BKN) initiates contact with Butler (MIA) that affects his ability to control the pass.
Griffin (BKN) briefly clamps Adebayo's (MIA) arm but immediately releases and does not affect his ability to defend the play.
Lowry (MIA) makes marginal contact with Irving (BKN) as he cleanly deflects the pass away.
Thomas (BKN) commits a take foul on Tucker (MIA).
